$b$ and $q$. The implied values of $\\theta_c$ (or $\\theta_{min}$) and\n$\\theta_{max}$ are close to the current observational limits. The true GRB rate\nfor the USJ model is found to be $R_{GRB}(z=0)=0.86^{+0.14}_{-0.05} Gpc^{-3}\nyr^{-1}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Jul 2004 20:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2005 23:58:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
