 the soliton sector of the original model and turns out to be the\nmaster Lagrangian describing the GMT and GSG models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Jul 2004 20:22:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
